rtant to put things into a longer-term perspective. In the case of UGI, the stock</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305707642/image_1305707642.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743410-ugi-corporation-winning-combination-of-high-yield-and-low-valuation", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 00:05:51"}, {"id": "4743407", "title": "Protara: Six-Month NMIBC Treatment Data Bodes Well For Mid-2025 Catalyst", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487041655/image_487041655.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Scientists working in modern laboratory\" data-id=\"487041655\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5120px\" height=\"3413px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487041655/image_487041655.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487041655/image_487041655.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487041655/image_487041655.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487041655/image_487041655.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487041655/image_487041655.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487041655/image_487041655.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487041655/image_487041655.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487041655/image_487041655.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Morsa Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Protara Therapeutics</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TARA\" title=\"Protara Therapeutics, Inc.\">TARA</a></span>) was able to report positive phase 2 results using its drug TARA-002 to treat high-risk non-muscle invasive bladder cancer [NMIBC] patients. This mid-stage study is known as ADVANCED-2 and used this drug to treat these</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487041655/image_487041655.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743407-protara-treatment-data-bodes-well-for-mid-2025-catalyst", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 23:55:24"}, {"id": "4743405", "title": "Archer Aviation: Bullish Future Despite Stellantis Turmoil", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155397246/image_2155397246.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"EVTOL Aircraft Landing On Rooftop Helipad In City\" data-id=\"2155397246\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"768px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155397246/image_2155397246.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155397246/image_2155397246.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155397246/image_2155397246.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155397246/image_2155397246.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155397246/image_2155397246.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155397246/image_2155397246.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155397246/image_2155397246.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155397246/image_2155397246.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">peepo/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In July 2024<span class=\"highlighted_text\">, I covered Archer Aviation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ACHR\" title=\"Archer Aviation Inc.\">ACHR</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4702299-why-did-archer-aviation-stock-soar\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4702299-why-did-archer-aviation-stock-soar\" target=\"_blank\">with a buy rating</a></span> after it cleared several milestones. Since then, the stock is up more than 85% and is up 128% since <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4697866-archer-aviation-stock-soars-balancing-risks-and-commercial-success\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4697866-archer-aviation-stock-soars-balancing-risks-and-commercial-success\" target=\"_blank\">my buy rating from a month earlier</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155397246/image_2155397246.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743405-archer-aviation-bullish-future-despite-stellantis-turmoil", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 23:43:28"}, {"id": "4743402", "title": "Tarsus Pharmaceuticals: Early Rollout Exceeding Expectations", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Life Science Investing\" data-id=\"155151969\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"715px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536