" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A candy store museum in Hershey, Pennsylvania\" data-id=\"1164904198\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Cheri Alguire</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>I like <strong>The Hershey Company (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HSY\" title=\"The Hershey Company\">HSY</a></span>)</strong>, as the title of my most recent <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4697143-going-coco-for-hersheys-a-path-to-double-digit-returns-for-this-dividend-gem\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4697143-going-coco-for-hersheys-a-path-to-double-digit-returns-for-this-dividend-gem\" target=\"_blank\">article</a> on June 3 had the bullish title, <em>\"Going Coco For Hershey's: A Path To Double-Digit Returns For This Dividend Gem.\" </em></p> <p>As it turns out, I'm not</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1164904198/image_1164904198.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743398-candy-crush-hersheys-m-and-a-buzz-is-just-the-cherry-on-top", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 23:19:12"}, {"id": "4743395", "title": "THW: Revisiting The 11.8% Healthcare Yielder As Thesis Plays Out", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Medical Exam\" data-id=\"1345550980\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">You Have A Case Of Yielditis. Keep Hand Away From Fist.</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">filadendron/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We first wrote about abrdn World Healthcare Fund (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/THW\" title=\"abrdn World Healthcare Fund\">THW</a></span>) 18 months back. We saw an unwarranted optimism on the fund coupled with faulty logic that made it a target for showing \"the other side\". While we have used some creative titles, this one</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345550980/image_1345550980.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743395-thw-revisiting-the-11-percent-healthcare-yielder-as-thesis-plays-out", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 23:14:36"}, {"id": "4743391", "title": "Alaska Airlines Stock Surges 15% On Bullish Outlook", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Alaska Airlines Boeing 737.\" data-id=\"1523412783\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1136px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DaveAlan</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Alaska Airli<span class=\"highlighted_text\">nes (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ALK\" title=\"Alaska Air Group, Inc.\">ALK</a></span>) h</span>as released its strategy update ahead of its Investor Day and investors seem to like what the company presented as the stock is trading 14% higher at the time of writing. In this report, I will be reviewing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743391-alaska-airlines-stock-surges-15-percent-on-bullish-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 23:03:13"}, {"id": "4743390", "title": "L3Harris Is Likely To Benefit From Increased Defense Spending Amid U.S.-China Tensions", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Leadership\" data-id=\"501650629\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"853px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/